WEBVTT

00:00:01.490 --> 00:00:15.220
Entering the synagogue for three months he spoke with boldness, giving talks and

00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:20.339
reasoning persuasively about the kingdom of God. But when some stubbornly

00:00:20.339 --> 00:00:30.649
refused to believe, speaking injuriously about the way before the crowd, he

00:00:30.649 --> 00:00:45.600
withdrew from them, giving talks daily in the school auditorium of

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:56.490
tyrannis. This went on for two years so that all those living in the province

00:00:56.490 --> 00:01:08.840
of Asia heard the word of the Lord, both Jews and Greeks.
